><br>As fer da low level equipment, der ibs so much stuff sellin fer so cheap out der nowadays, der really ibs no such ting as an &quot;untwinked&quot; character der anymore.  Once yoo can affords dem, picks up some crusty or crafted pieces fer yer coverins (aldoh make shur yoo pick up crusty legs over crafted legs, da +16 stam ibs much more beneficial dan da few stats on da crafted legs n' da extra 2 ac)  Also, if yoo not habs much money, yoo can probably buys a langseax er 2 really cheap, maybe 10 pp each er sumtin like dat.<br><br>Anyways, gud luck ter yoo!<br> <p><center><img src=http://extremeannihilation.nimueserver.com/images/cj_sig.gif border=0><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=221997" target="_blank"><font size="2">My Profile</font></a></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ujonnaspovar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jonnas Povar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 125<br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/15/02 7:26:23 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=944.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Troll Question</span><hr size=1> If you're gonna twink with finesteel, go on and twink with crafted/crusty, It'll probly cost about the same nowadays <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=69159">Jonnas Incognitto</a><BR>Worst equipped 54 human warrior on Povar<BR>Risen Phoenix<BR><a href="http://www.gaijindesign.com/lawriemalen/jedi" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.gaijindesign.com/lawriemalen/jedi/anakin.jpg" width="285" height="123" border="0"><br>:: how jedi are you? ::</